latestIgtvVideos.title: Curls for Beginners with @alantrumanofficial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sure my life isn’t perfect, but my curls are 🙈😉

Hey guys so I tried @alantrumanofficial ‘s Argan Gold Ceramic Curler and honestly I’m in love!! 
For a beginner like me it was quite difficult to do a basic curl but this curler is so easy to use and the best thing is it gets hot in no time and the Argan oil infused barrel gives my hair lustrous shine all day long!
Rate my first attempt at curls from 1 to 10 in comments 🙈
.
.
Grab yours on @mynykaa and @amazondotin at pretty amazing discounts.
